<div class="card text-center">
  <div class="card-header">
  Hai bisogno di informazioni o vuoi acquistare un gioco? 
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Riempi il form sottostante per farcelo sapere, sarai ricontattato il prima possibile</h5>
    <p class="card-text">Nota: le spedizioni sono per ora limitate all'Italia</p>
  </div>
</div>
<form>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
      <label for="inputName">Nome</label>
      <input type="text" id="firstname" class="form-control" placeholder="Mario">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
      <label for="inputSurname">Cognome</label>
      <input type="text" id="lastname" class="form-control" placeholder="Rossi">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
      <label for="inputAddress">Indirizzo</label>
      <input type="text" id="address" class="form-control" placeholder="via Roma 12">
    </div>
    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
      <label for="inputCity">Citt√†</label>
      <input type="text" id="city" class="form-control" placeholder="Reggio Emilia">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="inputEmail">Email</label>
    <input type="text" id="email" class="form-control" placeholder="dktBoardGame@gmail.com">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="inputRequests">Richieste</label>
    <input type="text" id="requests" class="form-control" placeholder="Collaborazioni/tempi di consegna/ecc.">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="form-check">
      <input onclick="subscribe()" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="gridCheck">
      <label class="form-check-label" for="gridCheck">
        Iscriviti alla newsletter
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a onclick="submit()" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" href="/submit">Invia</a>
</form>
<script src="./form.js"></script>
